{"tid":16350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"哥倫比亞墜機】決賽如期「上演」　球員沒法來球場仍滿座","createTime":"2016-12-01T11:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T13:33:47.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dd05cf679bfdd9b03892cf2392d2edbf10d31892","tid":16350,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:41:59.000Z","msg":"香港時間12月1日早上，原定舉行南美球會盃首回合，由哥倫比亞球會國民體育會，主場迎戰巴甲球會查比高恩斯。兩日前一場舉世震驚的空難慘劇，令乘搭飛機到哥倫比亞爭奪創會43年首個最高榮耀的查比高恩斯球員們，未能如期出現在國民體育會的綠茵場上。雖然比賽因此取消，但國民體育會仍組織球迷入場，就是為了哀悼本是對手的查比高恩斯。<br />\n<br />\n只見Atanasio Girardot運動場雖沒球員踢球，觀眾席卻坐滿了數萬名身穿綠或白衣的球迷，他們或手持蠟燭和手機閃光燈、或揮動白色手帕、或舉起查比高恩斯隊旗，異口同聲地為查比高恩斯的亡魂高歌，哀悼未能再現身賽場的球員名字。沒有球員比賽的場上，卻彷彿看到查比高恩斯的球員，在全場球迷齊心的打氣聲和淚水下，奮力馳騁。那一刻，全場都是查比高恩斯的球迷，無分彼此。<br />\n<br />\n[jpg]<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/media/images/298681/xlarge/eb3e7f1c4f578865a40360740dea3325.jpg[/jpg]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F298681%2Fxlarge%2Feb3e7f1c4f578865a40360740dea3325.jpg%5B%2Fjpg%5D&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=8b785e81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/media/images/298681/xlarge/eb3e7f1c4f578865a40360740dea3325.jpg[/jpg]</a><br />\n<br />\n[jpg]<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/media/images/298605/xlarge/66ae59ad19d269acefd3b5d40182d64c.jpg[/jpg]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F298605%2Fxlarge%2F66ae59ad19d269acefd3b5d40182d64c.jpg%5B%2Fjpg%5D&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=ad7a3cc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/media/images/298605/xlarge/66ae59ad19d269acefd3b5d40182d64c.jpg[/jpg]</a>"},{"pid":"561c03a40e2fc8f3260c2b28c9bed5ac336e124f","tid":16350,"uid":13835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T13:05:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"046eadc6373573c2d7c64906f1d9497cbddc197e","tid":16350,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T13:14:39.000Z","msg":"球迷仲多過球員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c29e2a68d2dc9152f13c430ca549bab0c5f0e524","tid":16350,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T13:17:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>球迷仲多過球員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n..."},{"pid":"9f1d423199e31e457db4343a49a215ec80478c8d","tid":16350,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T13:27:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n在一星期前，查比高恩斯22歲前鋒Tiago Da Rocha Vieira與隊友在一家酒店內，收到妻子寄來的禮物包裹。在片段中，見到Tiago Da Rocha Vieira坐近牆邊，細心地看妻子寫的一張字條，知道妻子有喜。他開心得跳起來，與隊友載歌載舞，慶祝自己快將榮升父親。空難發生後，他的家人才公開那段片段。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tb1qpEgFb2M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTb1qpEgFb2M&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=574c7bad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tb1qpEgFb2M</a>"},{"pid":"45e5aff53f65c5a44e35d43cbe7ae68348925c4a","tid":16350,"uid":31,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T13:28:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n在一星期前，查比高恩斯22歲前鋒Tiago Da Rocha Vieira與隊友在一家酒店內，收到妻子寄來的禮物包裹。在片段中，見到Tiago Da Rocha Vieira坐近牆邊，細心地看妻子寫的一張字條，知道妻子有喜。他開心得跳起來，與隊友載歌載舞，慶祝自己快將榮升父親。空難發生後，他的家人才公開那段片段。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tb1qpEgFb2M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTb1qpEgFb2M&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=574c7bad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tb1qpEgFb2M</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5f9d828b83e